{"tid":318744,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[真心求助]中三都升唔到可以點算?","createTime":"2017-07-12T10:08:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-12T12:36:21.000Z","uid":127815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"108291b6e1a89807d2796fae9f2cb9cf77ef1bc2","tid":318744,"uid":127815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T10:08:53.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲好，雖然DSE放榜都已經一片愁雲慘霧，但我細佬仲灰鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話說岩岩前幾日收到我某個auntie電話，話佢個仔即係我叫細佬果個，因為成績差而repeat左兩年form 2, 點知今年都仲係衰左，升唔到中三，要俾人踢出校<br />\n大佬呀，我第一時間心諗，是咪我個名咁樣呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n究竟有咩人種會連中二都要repeat, 仲要唔止repeat一年，仲要兩次重讀後結果都係升唔到中三，咩料呀玩野麼?!<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家佢學校搵左3間校名俾佢，叫佢去叩門申請，睇下人地收唔收佢讀中三，因為好似就算想讀ive職專果類都要至少中三學歷先收，請問各位過來人有無好提議/出路指點下佢?  感激不盡!<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我努力幫佢搵緊補習中，唉<br />\n不過聽佢學校社工講，話佢好似有讀寫障礙，都唔知係咪既，搞到我個auntie喊左好多日，佢寡母婆一日打兩份工養大個仔，呀細佬又偏偏唔爭氣，唉，聞者傷心，希望盡量幫到佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多謝大家既意見!<br />\n<br />\nps.問過下呀細佬，話有興趣想學廚，唔知堅定流定純粹敷衍我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8020c46c57eb7b2894a7e1beb5365ffd22c9325a","tid":318744,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T10:09:55.000Z","msg":"我會唔會識得佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28361f606a305b04774da78db1f9fe5c35891333","tid":318744,"uid":56731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T10:10:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/81DlosCueCL._SL1500_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-na.ssl-images-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FI%2F81DlosCueCL._SL1500_.jpg&h=3086d032&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"98190a15054a7a29ba0e1b2a55ca37ceb2c16937","tid":318744,"uid":1582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T10:10:40.000Z","msg":"細佬就是你"},{"pid":"caccffaf09c8a0c3bc335cbc5c19b2d3fd1cea80","tid":318744,"uid":7954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T10:11:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c2b79449c4f5c78d8648a8e56af85a9b2e10f3ff","tid":318744,"uid":127815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T10:13:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我會唔會識得佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n喂巴打講堅架? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你間學校係邊區架?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n喂唔好俾佢知我係度出post呀驚hurt到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8028722188ebac78eaf1f72380eb0a5b30505694","tid":318744,"uid":127815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T10:13:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細佬就是你</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 老娘當年高考中化有A架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5c468e5a909f7d4e5763adbc5ab3e38093996e6","tid":318744,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T10:14:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我會唔會識得佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n喂巴打講堅架? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你間學校係邊區架?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n喂唔好俾佢知我係度出post呀驚hurt到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgm